      <title outputclass="H3_1_9" class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">49.604</ph> Release of excess funds under terminated contracts.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p otherprops="Body" outputclass="Body" class="- topic/p ">The following format shall be used to recommend the release of excess funds under terminated contracts, except if the contracting office retains responsibility for settlement of the termination:</p>
         <p otherprops="Body_Alternate_NoIndent"
            outputclass="Body_Alternate_NoIndent"
            class="- topic/p ">
            <xref otherprops="SmallCaps" class="- topic/term "/>: Termination Contracting Officer __________ [address]</p>
         <p id="d2962e21" class="- topic/p ">
            <term otherprops="SmallCaps" class="- topic/term ">To</term>: Contracting office ______________[address]</p>
         <p id="d2962e27" class="- topic/p ">
            <term otherprops="SmallCaps" class="- topic/term ">Subj</term>: Terminated Contract No ________ with _______ [Contractor]</p>
         <p otherprops="Body_Alternate_NoIndent"
            outputclass="Body_Alternate_NoIndent"
            class="- topic/p ">Refs:</p>
         <p otherprops="Body_Alternate_List1"
            outputclass="Body_Alternate_List1"
            class="- topic/p ">(a) [<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Cite termination notice and effective date.</i>]</p>
         <p otherprops="Body_Alternate_List1"
            outputclass="Body_Alternate_List1"
            class="- topic/p ">(b) [<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Cite prior letters releasing excess funds, if any.</i>]</p>
         <p otherprops="Body_Alternate_List2"
            outputclass="Body_Alternate_List2"
            class="- topic/p ">(1) Referenced termination notice, ____ [<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">insert</i> “completely” <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">or</i> “partially”] terminated contract __________.</p>
         <p otherprops="Body_Alternate_List2"
            outputclass="Body_Alternate_List2"
            class="- topic/p ">(2) Based on the best information available, it is estimated that the gross settlement cost will be $_____ The amount available for release as excess to the contract is $___. Any payments previously made to the Contractor for terminated items have been considered in arriving at the above amounts.</p>
         <p otherprops="Body_Alternate_NoIndent"
            outputclass="Body_Alternate_NoIndent"
            class="- topic/p ">[<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">If prior letters recommending release of excess funds are cited, use the following as paragraph 2:</i>
         </p>
         <p otherprops="Body_Alternate_NoIndent"
            outputclass="Body_Alternate_NoIndent"
            class="- topic/p ">The estimated settlement costs previously reported by reference (b) in the amount of $____ are revised. On the best evidence now available, it is estimated that the settlement costs will be $___ The additional amount available for release is $_____.]</p>
         <p otherprops="Body_Alternate_List2"
            outputclass="Body_Alternate_List2"
            class="- topic/p ">(3) The related appropriations and amounts involved are:</p>
